Contains minor recipes and break downs for how to use {{Alchemy Ingredient Bundles}}.

After some extensive reading, one could learn to use those bundles with an {{Alchemy Kit}} to create potions.

Due to the complexity of usage of the ingredient bundles, it can take sometime to acquire more complicated recipes and despite the recipes here-in, actually learning them without this book and being able to create them prove difficult.

# Recipe Appendix

The recipes here-in can eventually be learned with some effort, most involving a key ingredient. Until learned, the general recipe is the key ingredient plus 10 {{Alchemy Ingredient Bundles}}:
+ Water Breathing Potion: {{Aigua Leaf}}
+ Minor Healing Potion: {{Sana Leaf}}
+ Poison Remedy: {{Venom Sac}}
+ Smoke Bomb: {{Autus Leaf}}

