The head of Filala's corpse.

Last cast of talk with the dead:  
{{@Alucevum 7, 319}}

[ Last Spoken to on {{@Alucevum 8, 319}} ]

After dying while chauffering {{Mrs. Dinoir}} from the city of {{Curell}}, his body was later collected after bing found invisible hidden in bushes near the side of the road.

After being taken back to the {{warden Garrison}}, the party was able to pick his bodyout from the still invisible corpses thanks to talking to {{Mrs. Dinoir}} and asked him some questions after severing his head so that they could use {{Speak with the Dead}} and ask some additional questions later.

Questions from {{@Alucevum 8, 319}}:
+ {{@Have you ever seen or heard of a snake/humanoid hybrid?}} {{ No, can’t say that I have}}
+ {{@What do you remember before you passed away?}} {{ Trying to get Mrs. Dinoir to safety}}
+ {{@Do you know who the investigators Mrs. Dinoir hired?}} {{ Athis and Cesis}}
+ {{@Was there anything unusual about the carriage you drove yesterday?}} {{ Nope, handled just fine}}
+ {{@Do you know anything about a powerful invisibility spell?}} {{ No, don’t know much about it}}

